431
00:48:21,200 --> 00:48:23,350
Ty si Cha Sung Il, nie?

432
00:48:23,620 --> 00:48:24,910
Dnes je Deň D.

433
00:48:25,210 --> 00:48:29,260
Som rada, že som do Cheol Sua
