434
00:48:29,890 --> 00:48:32,250
- Máš ho rada tak veľmi?
- Áno.

435
00:48:32,920 --> 00:48:34,370
Prečo ste ma zavolali?

436
00:48:34,770 --> 00:48:37,420
Je tam niekto?

437
00:48:40,110 --> 00:48:42,080
Nikdy si ku mne nebol úprimný.

438
00:48:42,080 --> 00:48:43,340
Aký by v tom bol rozdiel?

439
00:48:43,340 --> 00:48:45,540
Stále ju máš rád?

